pe) collapses to a flat schema:geo edge; non-displayable/superseded observations are suppressed; the Copyright relator (year, notice, status) collapses to a flat schema:copyrightHolder edge; the structured Copyright relator (holder, year, status) collapses to a flat schema:copyrightNotice edge; the Copyright relator (holder, notice, status) collapses to a flat schema:copyrightYear edge; the Skill/Occupation distinction in credentialFor collapses to schema:competencyRequired; the issuer organization relator collapses to a flat schema:recognizedBy edge; the currency reference frame collapses to its ISO 4217 / ticker code; schema:currenciesAccepted is a free-text code list; the member document is REUSED as the schema:DataDownload node; its GMEOW typing drops; the feed's ordered membership flattens to schema:dataFeedElement; each member is REUSED as a schema:DataFeedItem (no item-wrapper mint); the death Participation (role, period, confidence, standpoint) is dropped; only the principal's death instant survives; the death Participation detail drops; only the principal's deathplace survives; the subOrganizationOf hierarchy and any contested succession/standpoint claims collapse to a flat schema:department edge; depiction context, audience, period, and authority dropped; only the depicted entity survives; description withheld when entity is not explicitly eligible for consumerPublicSite; the destruction event's place, participants, and standpoint are dropped; only the instant survives as schema:dissolutionDate; authority provenance, confidence, standpoint, and exact-vs-close match distinction collapse to a schema.org identity URL; skos:closeMatch authority links are not emitted; none for the tag triple — propertyID/value/name carry the full EXIF tag; the gmeow:ExifTag node is reused as the PropertyValue; the creation event's place, participants, and standpoint are dropped; only the instant survives as schema:foundingDate; the uncertainty band (gmeow:latestEnd) and the gmeow:temporalPrecision qualifier are dropped; only the earliest bound survives as a single schema:startDate; orientation + sexAssignedAtBirth dropped; sex/gender conflated; modality, veridicality, confidence, standpoint poset, and the reified statement content dropped; verdicts ride as per-review ClaimReview nodes (mapSchemaClaimReview) preserving the data's epistemic shape — attributed stays authored, anonymous stays anonymous, nothing computed; appearance only when the evidence spine is complete; the specialized GMEOW whole-to-part subproperty, if any, is collapsed to generic schema:hasPart; the siteType distinction (headquarters/branch/registered) is dropped; the target node's own Place projection preserves geographic detail; tag IRI lost; only label text emitted; displayable false tags suppressed; the article's title doubles as its headline (schema.org's article idiom); jurisdiction and any standpoint/validity detail on the record drop; schema's PropertyValue carries only the scheme/value/url/name quad; the record's rdfs:label is its display name; the depiction's context/period/audience drop; the entity gains schema:image pointing at the depicting MediaObject; unit (pixels) is implicit in schema:height when emitted as integer; MediaObject also covers audio and video; the ImageObject projection is lossy for non-image media; unit (pixels) is implicit in schema:width when emitted as integer; the first-class gmeow:Language collapses to its BCP-47 / ISO 639-1 tag string; script and variety detail drop; only ISIC-V4-scheme classifications are emitted; NAICS and other schemes are dropped; only NAICS-scheme classifications are emitted; ISIC and other schemes are dropped; the code is emitted as a plain literal; contribution period, provenance, confidence drop; the Membership relator (organization, period, role, confidence, standpoint) collapses to a flat schema:jobTitle literal; contested membership claims are not distinguished; CEFR/ILR/ACTFL level and skill modality dropped; only LEI-scheme identifiers are emitted; other schemes (ROR, company registration, Wikidata) are dropped in this projection; the location's type distinction (Place vs VirtualLocation vs StorageLocation) is preserved by the target node's own rdf:type projection, but the locatedAt relation itself loses the structural subproperty (storedIn, physicalPlace); contribution period, provenance, confidence, degree drop; the Capacity relator (provenance, unit, temporal scope, standpoint) collapses to a flat schema:maximumAttendeeCapacity integer; non-displayable/superseded capacities are suppressed; restricted to gmeow:Place to avoid projecting byte capacities from StorageLocation; microblog narrows to schema's SocialMediaPosting (no microblog subclass); provider (string, no faithful Organization node), context window, and training cutoff dropped; the card/agent distinction collapses onto the agent; the event's open kind value, temporal fuzziness and participation detail drop; only the action shape with its origin survives; the event's open kind value, temporal fuzziness and participation detail drop; only the action shape with its destination survives; the WEMI spine collapses; track-level frame-relative content and declared losses are lost; recording event provenance, take/overdub structure, and standpoint-indexed performance claims collapse to a flat schema:MusicRecording; the WEMI spine collapses: Work, Expression, and Manifestation are flattened into one schema:MusicComposition; realization mode and notation frame are lost; non-displayable names (deadnames) dropped; the NetworkAddress frame, type, provenance, and standpoint are dropped; only the URL string survives; standpoint, confidence, temporal scope, suppression state, aboutness, tagging dropped; Comment-specific typing collapsed to schema:NoteDigitalDocument (rdflib UNION limit); the Occupancy relator (provenance, unit, temporal scope, standpoint) collapses to a flat schema:occupancy integer; non-displayable/superseded occupancies are suppressed; restricted to gmeow:Place to avoid projecting byte occupancies from StorageLocation; the offering is REUSED as the schema:Offer node; price/availability detail is not modelled; the spec is REUSED as schema:OpeningHoursSpecification; price/validity detail is not modelled; the Participation's period / confidence / evidence / standpoint collapse to a flat schema:organizer edge; the page's other isAbout mentions drop; only the principal subject becomes mainEntity, with its inverse mainEntityOfPage on the subject; the page→site mereology is the breadcrumb hierarchy; schema:BreadcrumbList's ordered ListItem wrapper is a presentation concern over this isPartOf chain (P12); the specialized GMEOW parthood subproperty, if any, is collapsed to generic schema:isPartOf; the PaymentMethod individual collapses to its label text; schema:paymentAccepted is a free-text list; the Participation's period / confidence / evidence / standpoint collapse to a flat schema:performer edge; namePurpose (endonym/exonym/superseded) is ignored; every displayable name is emitted as schema:name. The consumer receives all co-equal claims without privileging.; exonym selection is locale-relative; precise coordinates coarsened to the enclosing region at gmeow:coarsenTo level (privacy generalization, P10); competing-standpoint names and names with specific purposes dropped; projection frame = endonym-preferred; co-equal exonyms projected as schema:alternateName; non-displayable/superseded and competing-standpoint names dropped; the Post (seat ⟂ holder) and Membership relator collapse to a flat schema:roleName; contested membership claims are not distinguished; the WebPage→ProfilePage refinement is the defined-class inference (page principally about an Agent); schema gets the bare ProfilePage typing; schema:programmingLanguage points at the first-class language (itself projected to schema:ComputerLanguage by mapSchemaProgrammingLanguage); only the project→language edge